Courtenay Foote https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Courtenay_Foote 0 Courtenay Foote (22 November 1878 – 4 May 1925) was an English actor of the silent era. He appeared in 59 films between 1910 and 1924. He was born in Harrogate, West Riding of Yorkshire and died in Italy. Courtenay_Foote ( 22_November_1878 – 4_May_1925 ) was an_English_actor of the_silent_era .
